```mermaid
flowchart LR
  Browser([Browser<br/>https://www.google.com]) -->|1. DNS lookup| DNS[DNS<br/>(root → .com → auth)]
  DNS -->|returns IP| Browser
  Browser -->|2. TCP connect (SYN) to IP:443| Internet(Internet / Network)
  Internet -->|3. Encrypted TLS handshake (HTTPS)| Firewall[Firewall / WAF]
  Firewall -->|4. Forward to| LB[Load Balancer]
  LB -->|5. Route to| WebServer[Web Server<br/>(HTTP/S)]
  WebServer -->|6. Forward dynamic request| AppServer[Application Server]
  AppServer -->|7. Query| Database[(Database)]
  Database -->|8. Result| AppServer
  AppServer -->|9. HTML/CSS/JS response| WebServer
  WebServer -->|10. Response through LB| LB
  LB -->|11. Through Firewall| Firewall
  Firewall -->|12. Encrypted response over TLS| Browser

  classDef box fill:#f4f7fb,stroke:#2b7cff,stroke-width:1px;
  class Browser,DNS,Internet,Firewall,LB,WebServer,AppServer,Database box;
```
